 class=m><span class=title> Re: i didnt say...</span><hr size=1> Persoanlly I use a 2hn sword for my backstab chain which is a big end hog but then i quickly switch to Sword and shield for increased speed of swing.  After I hit them with the backstab chain I am able to have them down to about 1/8 of the mobs life then i only need to connect a few more times and they are dead.  Yes as a SB I can solo yellows but only because I keep sword up with my level and I poured points into Str to bring it up to 80 and then put 10 points each into dex and quick.  at about level 15 my str should hit 85.  85 is the magic number for damaged bonuses after 85 you get a str modifier and your damage increases.  Currtently I am specing CS and Sword,after CS hits 21 then going sword and stealth.<br>
<br>
I find using Sword and shield favorable to doing dual wield as you can block blows which saves damage.  IMHO DW sucks in this game because it gains are marginal at best.  I can do more and take less using 2h followed by a weapon changing in mid combat to a faster 1 hnd sword and shield. <p><font size=4 color=Green><b>Ansuz Odhinnson</font></b>
